OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,FEighteen-year-olds will be allowed to
OL,7,Fdrive trains amid concerns over driver
OL,8,Fshortages.
OL,10,FThe minimum age to take on the role in
OL,11,FBritain is to be lowered from 20, the
OL,12,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) has
OL,13,Fannounced.
OL,15,FRail services are frequently disrupted
OL,16,Fbecause several operators rely on
OL,17,Fdrivers voluntarily working extra
OL,18,Fshifts to run timetabled services.
