OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,FThe size of the workforce is forecast
OL,7,Fto decline over the coming years, as
OL,8,Fdrivers are retiring at a faster rate
OL,9,Fthan new ones are being recruited.
OL,11,FThe DfT said a consultation on
OL,12,Flowering the minimum age for drivers `
OL,13,Fcarried out last year by the
OL,14,FConservative government ` received
OL,15,F"overwhelming support from across the
OL,16,Findustry".
