OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're taking bold action to
OL,8,Fimprove train services and unlock
OL,9,Fthousands of jobs.
OL,11,F"We're committed to getting the
OL,12,Feconomy moving and a big part of that
OL,13,Fis getting young people into the
OL,14,Fworkforce, putting them on track for a
OL,15,Fskilled and fulfilling career which
OL,16,Fwill boost growth across the country
OL,17,Fand help deliver our Plan for Change.
