OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,F"We're future-proofing our railways
OL,7,Fagainst delays and cancellations
OL,8,Fcaused by a shortage of drivers,
OL,9,Fensuring that we can provide reliable,
OL,10,Fpassenger-focused train journeys under
OL,11,FGreat British Railways (GBR) for
OL,12,Fdecades to come."
OL,14,FThe Government plans to establish GBR
OL,15,Fas a new public sector body which will
OL,16,Foversee rail infrastructure management
OL,17,Fand train operation.
