OL,3,CMinimum age for train drivers to be
OL,4,Clowered to 18 amid shortage
OL,6,FMick Whelan, general secretary of
OL,7,Ftrain drivers' union Aslef, said: "At
OL,8,Fthe moment, young people who want to
OL,9,Fbecome train drivers leave school or
OL,10,Fcollege at 18, get other jobs, and we
OL,11,Fmiss out as an industry as they don't
OL,12,Fwait around until they turn 20 to find
OL,13,Fa career."
OL,15,FHe added that the new policy will
OL,16,F"increase diversity in the driver's
OL,17,Fcab" as well as encouraging more young
OL,18,Fpeople to take on the role.
